  <h2>谁读这本书?</h2>
  <div class="indent" id="collector">

    

<div class="">
    
    <div class="ll"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/52543767/"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u52543767-18.jpg" class="pil" alt="肖斯凯" /></a></div>
    <div style="padding-left:60px"><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/people/52543767/">肖斯凯</a><br/>
